    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a reliable daily driver for someone who doesn't mind some cosmetic and mechanical character. The exterior shows its age with noticeable paint fading on the hood and roof, along with several scuffs and a small ding on the passenger door. Inside, the upholstery is intact but shows moderate wear and some staining on the carpets. Mechanically, the car runs and drives, though it will likely need a suspension tune-up and new tires in the near future. It has been a dependable car, but it is priced to reflect that it is not in showroom condition.",
