    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been meticulously cared for by its previous owner. The engine starts up immediately and runs smoothly, showing no signs of leaks or unusual noises, and the transmission shifts through all gears effortlessly. The interior is clean and smoke-free, though you may find minor surface wear on the driver's seat and some light scratches on the exterior paint consistent with careful use. All major electronic features are fully functional, making this a reliable and comfortable choice for a daily driver.",
