    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary vehicle, currently held in showroom condition. This specimen has been curated with fastidious attention to detail, manifesting in an unblemished exterior and an interior that retains its original factory integrity. Every mechanical system has undergone a comprehensive diagnostic review to ensure performance remains within peak operational parameters. This is an investment-grade acquisition for the individual who demands uncompromising quality and aesthetic perfection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
